headline: Is TPR Positioned to Deliver Strong Growth Despite Tariff Headwinds?
summary: Tapestry posts record FY25 results. It reveals the FY26 outlook for growth in revenues, EPS and shareholder returns despite tariff pressures.

headline: Capri Holdings: Attractive In The Short Run But Risky In The Long Run
summary: Capri Holdings (CPRI) has underperformed the S&P 500 significantly, with recent losses exacerbated by the failed acquisition by Tapestry (TPR).
